Package domosaics.ui.views.view

Interface Summary
View The View interface defining all methods which can be applied to each view.
 

Class Summary
AbstractView AbstractView is the basic implementation for the View interface.
ViewActionManager The view specific action manager extending the DefaultMenuActionManager from MenuReader.
ViewInfo Class containing all needed information to create a new view or tool.
ViewPanel Class ViewPanel is the basic class for embedding views, such as DomainView into the user interface.
